summary: it’s really annoying to hear that andi and buffy are going to be fighting for the entirety of our tyrus episodes. this means...
body: it’s really annoying to hear that andi and buffy are going to be fighting for the entirety of our tyrus episodes. this means that yet again we’ll see cyrus and buffy’s friendship flourish as she helps him with his sexuality struggles while andi remains oblivious. they really do a terrible job of making it seem like andi and cyrus actually like each other and they’re not just friends via buffy. i just want andi to help cyrus for once so their relationship seems less one sided.

summary: I know we’re all hung up on the ‘coming clean’ part of this synopsis but ... ‘after an encouraging talk Buffy’ ??? Like that’s...
body:
I know we’re all hung up on the ‘coming clean’ part of this synopsis but … ‘after an encouraging talk Buffy’ ??? Like that’s the part that excites/gives me the most hope for this story line

Because it means either

1) Buffy knows what it’s about and so it’s not likely connected to the episode before as she has a separate plot line (unless Cyrus runs to her to talk about his dangerous experience)

Or

2) Buffy talks to Cyrus about her relationship with Walker which spurs him to come clean about a certain relationship (or feelings) that he’s been hiding
